snippet.title: Prune - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
***Out now on iOS, Android, and Windows!*** 
App Store: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/prune/id972319818?mt=8&at=1000l629&ct=yt
Google Play: http://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.Polyculture.Prune
Windows Store/Phone: https://www.microsoft.com/store/apps/9nblggh20g05

Prune is a love letter to trees. A game about the beauty and joy of cultivation.

http://www.prunegame.com
http://www.twitter.com/prunegame

Music by Kyle Preston: http://www.kylepreston.com
